Take 3 spoons of rice

31
00:09:37,685 --> 00:09:43,652
1 Liter of water

32
00:09:56,463 --> 00:10:06,447
Water the orchid with rice water every 2 weeks

33
00:10:12,635 --> 00:10:22,611
Rice water helps stimulate growth and adds many nutrients to help baby orchids grow quickly

34
00:10:47,355 --> 00:10:57,337
Spray a moisturizing mist with water when the surface feels dry

